projects.title: CoupCoupon
projects.description: A comprehensive platform for managing coupons and deals, featuring role-based access control for admins, companies, and customers. Built with modern web technologies. This platform enables admins to manage users and deals, companies to create and manage coupons, and customers to browse and redeem available offers.
